description: EmergencyUnlock: Records of emergency unlock activations on Ericsson RAN cells, including timestamps, cell identifiers, activation status, and remaining activations.  `dateTime`: Timestamp of record; `Area_Name`: RAN area name; `CellId`: Unique cell identifier; `Id2`: Duplicate of CellId; `Id3`: Redundant identifier (always 1); `Id4`: Redundant identifier (always 1); `vsDataType`: Data type identifier; `vsDataFormatVersion`: Data format version; `EmergencyUnlock.activationsLeft`: Number of emergency unlocks remaining; `EmergencyUnlock.expiration`: Expiration time (currently empty); `EmergencyUnlock.activationState`: Current activation state; `EmergencyUnlock.emergencyUnlockId`: Unique emergency unlock identifier.
